## Ecosystem Distribution Model

Kivode+ is maintained as a Reference Implementation and supports an ecosystem of Independent Fork projects.

Developers may:
- create independent versions,
- rename their versions,
- publish their own repositories.

All distributions and derivative works must continue to comply with the non-commercial restrictions in this License.

To be considered for official Directory Listing, developers must submit their projects for review:
https://kivode.com/apps/submit
